title: GeorgeR.R.Martin-SongOfIceAndFire1-AGameOfThrones
description:
George R. R. Martin - Song Of Ice And Fire 1 - A Game Of Thrones

A 32kbit version of the audiobook. Much better quality than the 16kbit version that is now available as part of the whole series.
I downloaded it a year or more ago and found now that only the low quality version is available, so I upload it again.
It would be great if someone did the same for the second part as well (A Clash of Kings).
